1
00:00:00,287 --> 00:00:01,347
Previously on "Invasion"...

2
00:00:01,348 --> 00:00:03,088
Is this your baby?
No.

3
00:00:03,099 --> 00:00:04,918
Why did you kill your mother-in-law?

4
00:00:05,179 --> 00:00:07,567
If she wanted the baby,
she could have had it.

5
00:00:07,568 --> 00:00:09,752
She was forcing it on me.

6
00:00:10,134 --> 00:00:11,545
What really happened to you
that night in the water?

7
00:00:11,546 --> 00:00:12,368
Do you know?

8
00:00:12,369 --> 00:00:13,351
Well, you have children, too,

9
00:00:13,592 --> 00:00:15,595
don't you think you, at least,
owe it to them to find out?

10
00:00:15,596 --> 00:00:17,420
I don't want you seeing my daughter anymore.

11
00:00:17,420 --> 00:00:18,420
She's not your type.

12
00:00:18,420 --> 00:00:19,233
What does he know?

13
00:00:19,233 --> 00:00:20,681
You have a lot to learn.

14
00:00:20,681 --> 00:00:22,485
There's a little work camp
down in the glades.

15
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:24,798
I'm gonna send you there
for a while, all right?

16
00:00:24,799 --> 00:00:27,021
I think you're in a lot of denial.

17
00:00:27,022 --> 00:00:29,551
You're just trying to control everything,

18
00:00:29,552 --> 00:00:32,382
trying to manage everyone, but you can't.

19
00:00:33,306 --> 00:00:34,619
You bastard!

20
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,752
So you two work everything out?

21
00:00:35,753 --> 00:00:37,280
She's a very special girl, sir.

22
00:00:37,281 --> 00:00:39,219
Yes, she is. She's also a very young girl.

23
00:00:39,220 --> 00:00:41,430
In many ways, she's a very naive girl.

24
00:00:41,431 --> 00:00:42,860
What happens in the water?

25
00:00:43,615 --> 00:00:44,212
I don't know.

26
00:00:44,213 --> 00:00:45,936
Why hasn't it happened to me?

27
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:47,677
Welcome to camp, darlin'.

28
00:00:47,678 --> 00:00:49,689
You're on the island of misfit toys, honey.

29
00:00:49,690 --> 00:00:51,543
Once we go through basic training,

30
00:00:51,945 --> 00:00:53,513
I'm comin' back with a vengeance.

31
00:00:55,909 --> 00:00:57,938
Invasion
